OL,4,CTrain named after Great Escape hero who
OL,5,C'inspired Steve McQueen'
OL,6, A World War Two pilot who was part of
OL,7, the Great Escape team is to have a
OL,8, train named after him.
OL,10,FWing Cdr Ken Rees was imprisoned in
OL,11,FStalag Luft III prisoner of war camp in
OL,12,FGermany and helped dig a tunnel that
OL,13,Fprisoners fled through in March 1944.
OL,15,FHe was caught in the shaft during the
OL,16,Fbreakout when it was discovered by a
OL,17,Fguard.
OL,19,FHe was said to have inspired Steve
OL,20,FMcQueen's character in the film based
OL,21,Fon their story, though he denied this.
